{"tid":1106252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台軍心戰大隊炮製投誠食品向解放軍招降","createTime":"2019-04-14T12:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T13:16:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"069eb9e99c0321ea2dc39f18f33bccbe4775fdf3","tid":1106252,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190414/large/1555238836_0769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190414%2Flarge%2F1555238836_0769.jpg&h=638757fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190414/large/1555239179_1038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190414%2Flarge%2F1555239179_1038.jpg&h=202e0a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣國防部心戰大隊製作「投誠食品」。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n台灣國防部心戰大隊製作「投誠食品」要招降共軍，大陸網民看到後留言：「我以為看到上世紀的新聞」、「現在2019，中國已經崛起了，趕緊回歸祖國吧」、「過來給你們發茶葉蛋！」<br />\n台灣當局製作大量「投誠食品」，示範台軍的心戰手段，這些食品在蛋卷、餅乾、即食麵、牛奶糖的包裝上，加印簡體字宣傳字句，要「共軍別抵抗，快投降」，包裝盒還印上「投降」地點的位置圖。「投誠風味方便麵」的包裝即印有「請保留此方便麵並放下武器，向xxxx軍投誠，我們保證提供熱水與安全。」<br />\n<br />\n國防部文宣心戰處長樓偉傑少將解釋，心戰宣傳內容強調民主自由的可貴，揚棄對專制統治的政權為主軸，針對中共從不放棄武力犯台，時時對台文攻武嚇的訊息進行有效的反制。他指，台軍配合戰場需要，結合台灣自由民主理念，從食品包裝到各種隨處可見的民生用品，都是心戰宣傳品可運用的素材，做到植基於平時，運用於戰時。<br />\n<br />\n大陸網民看後紛紛留言嘲笑：「我以為看到上世紀的新聞」、「現在2019，中國已經崛起了，趕緊回歸祖國吧」、「阿伯快趴下，阿共仔打過來了」、「做你的癡心妄想夢吧」、「坐井觀天，台軍已經不曉得這是啥時代了」、「不加腸又不加蛋，不投降。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190414/59488013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F59488013&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=468ff00f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F59488013&h=649c92d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190414/59488013</a>"},{"pid":"ea23658902e5562b5b3416a19314845727cbc040","tid":1106252,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"有得食班支那仔咪又係狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f59d3a9583329472dad69fe25da8418957d874c","tid":1106252,"uid":43041,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:47:31.000Z","msg":"中華民國國旗都打格仔，垃圾蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ebf98371217c9bd4e4113e20d99ad835dac970","tid":1106252,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":27,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:48:52.000Z","msg":"講真，大陸d杯麵真係幾好食，我番intern嗰陣同d鬼佬講我地香港人都中意食康師傅，仲特登走去d新落成嗰啲屋邨嘅士多買左幾碗俾佢食"},{"pid":"6f014f056d39005044eb18d9dc65792d4bac8208","tid":1106252,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"fake news?"},{"pid":"3bbc27be82a3a8a82258c38ce9784ff6cc774f5b","tid":1106252,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ebf98371217c9bd4e4113e20d99ad835dac970","tid":1106252,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":27,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:48:52.000Z","msg":"講真，大陸d杯麵真係幾好食，我番intern嗰陣同d鬼佬講我地香港人都中意食康師傅，仲特登走去d新落成嗰啲屋邨嘅士多買左幾碗俾佢食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:51:56.000Z","msg":"新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0f1af2fb45ef62dc360aafdb03ca63553dc376","tid":1106252,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f014f056d39005044eb18d9dc65792d4bac8208","tid":1106252,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"fake news?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rLuEo2IGPON.kHuK7ZY1fQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjkyO2g9NDYx/http://media.zenfs.com